      <title>多伦多有望成为 2022 年以来首家新外国矿业公司上市的“赢家”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/toronto-sees-win-in-first-new-foreign-miner-listing-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Paladin Energy Ltd. 登陆加拿大，标志着自 2022 年以来首次有大型外国矿业公司在多伦多证券交易所上市，而该交易所的新公司上市速度一直很慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/toronto-sees-win-in-first-new-foreign-miner-listing-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:01:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
