    <item>
      <title>欧盟有条件批准邦吉 82 亿美元 Viterra 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bunge-s-8-2-billion-viterra-deal-set-for-conditional-eu-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[邦吉全球公司 (Bunge Global SA) 计划斥资 82 亿美元收购 Viterra Inc.，该交易即将获得欧盟批准，此前两家公司做出的让步似乎已经平息了监管机构的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bunge-s-8-2-billion-viterra-deal-set-for-conditional-eu-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 13:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GE Vernova 计划在事故发生后对风力发电机叶片进行大规模检查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ge-vernova-identified-manufacturing-deviation-at-blade-factory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通用电气 Vernova 公司 (GE Vernova Inc.) 计划对公司生产的每一片海上风力涡轮机叶片进行重新检查，因为该公司发现，供应美国在建项目中最近发生断裂的零部件的工厂存在“材料偏差”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ge-vernova-identified-manufacturing-deviation-at-blade-factory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>家居用品零售商 Conn’s 因销售额下滑申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/retailer-conn-s-files-for-bankruptcy-following-sales-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[家具零售商 Conn’s Inc. 申请破产并计划关闭，原因是整合最近的收购事件遇到困难，加剧了销售滞后的痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/retailer-conn-s-files-for-bankruptcy-following-sales-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
